name: Small Giraffe Hook
description: Small Giraffe Hook is cast in non-leaded pewter and comes with four stainless steel screws to mount on a door or wall.  He measures 3" (H) x 1-1/4" (W) x 2-3/4" (D).  He's a sweet little giraffe and a great hook for any room in the house.  He's especially happy when he's near his mama, Large Giraffe Hook.

name: Large Giraffe Hook
description:
Large Giraffe Hook is cast in non-leaded pewter and comes with four stainless steels screws for mounting on a door or wall.  She is sturdy as well as graceful and measures  4-1/2 (H) x 1-1/2 (W) x 3-1/2 (D).

Large Giraffe and Small Giraffe Hooks look great together.  They stylishly hold up clothes for kids' bedrooms as well as aprons and brooms in the kitchen.

name: Ike Moose - American Wildlife Knob
description: Ike is cast in non-leaded pewter and comes with a 1" x 8-32 stainless steel machine screw for attaching him to a cabinet door or drawer.  He measures 2-1/4" x 1-1/2" x 2-3/4".  He's a sensitive moose, quite tasteful and very useful.

name: Ollie Elephant - African Animal Knob
description: Ollie is cast in non-leaded pewter and measures 1-3/4" x 2-1/2" x 2".  He comes with a 1" x 3-32 stainless steel machine screw for attaching to a cabinet door or drawer.  He looks great with his pals Rosie Rhino and Betty Hippo, but is commanding enough to make a statement all by himself.

name: Betty Hippo - African Animal Knob
description: Betty Hippo is cast in non-leaded pewter and measures 1-3/4" x 1" x 1-3/4".  This handsome hippo comes with a 1" x 3-32 stainless steel machine screw for mounting on a cabinet door or drawer.  In addition, a hanger screw is included to turn Betty into a hook.  Either way, knob or hook, Betty will cheer up your surroundings.

name: Rosie Rhino - African Animal Knob
description: Rosie is cast in non-leaded pewter and measures 2-1/4" x 1-1/2" x 2-3/4".  She comes with a 1" x 8-32 stainless machine screw for using her as a cabinet knob and a hanger screw if you'd like her to be used as a hook.  Either way, knob or hook, Rosie will make you smile.

name: Spencer Elephant Pull
description: Spencer is a lovely elephant head made from non-leaded pewter.  He comes with two stainless steel wood screws that affixes him to a door or drawer.  He measures 4-1/2" x 2-3/4" x 1-1/2".

name: People Pulls - Simone & Yves
description: Simone & Yves are two vertical door pulls.  They are French.  They are a couple.  If in domestic bliss, they face each other.  If at odds, they may be placed facing away from each other.  It's up to you.  Simone is 5" x 1-1/2" x 1-3/4" and Yves is 5" x 1" x 1-3/4".  Both are cast in non-leaded pewter and come with two 8-32 machine screws which are set 1" apart.  They work well in the bedroom.  As we said, they are French.  Price shown is for the pair.

name: Cubist Cat Knob
description: Cubist Cat is cast in non-leaded pewter and measures 1-1/4" x 1-1/4" x 1-1/2".  She comes with an 8-32 x 1" stainless steel machine screw for fastening to a cabinet door or drawer.

name: Big-Eyed Cat Knob
description: Big-Eyed Cat is cast in non-leaded pewter.  He measures 1-3/4" x 1-1/4" x 1-1/4" and comes with an 8-32 x 1" machine screw for attaching to a cabinet door or drawer.

name: Rodney - Medium Cat Head Knob
description: Rodney is amused by the world.  He doesn't quite know what to make of it all, but he goes with the flow.  He is cast in non-leaded pewter and measures 1-1/2" x 1-1/4" x 1".  He comes with an 8-32 x 1" stainless steel machine screw for affixing him to a door or drawer.  Rodney's got a good aura.

name: Mabel - Medium Cat Head Knob
description: Mabel is a cat with a great sense of humor.  She knows how to amuse herself and others as well.  She is cast in non-leaded pewter and measures 1-1/2" x 1-3/4" x 1-1/4".  Mabel comes with a 32-1" stainless steel machine screw for attaching her to a door or drawer.  With Mabel in the house, everything will be copacetic.

name: Slinky - Medium Cat Head Knob
description: Slinky grew up in a rough & tough neighborhood.  He has loads of street-smarts and charm.  Slinky measures 1-1/2" x 1-1/4" x 1" and is cast in non-leaded pewter.  He comes with one 8-32 x 1" stainless steel machine screw for attaching to a door or drawer.  You'll like Slinky...he's one cool cat!

name: Charlotte - Medium Cat Head Knob
description: Charlotte is one of four medium cat head knobs.  She thinks she is the alpha-cat and the other three let her think it's the truth.  Charlotte measures 1-1/2" x 2" x 1-1/2" and is cast in non-leaded pewter.  Charlotte comes with one 8-32 x 1" stainless steel machine screw for attaching to a door or drawer.

name: Sugar - Small Cat Head Knob
description: Sugar is cast in non-leaded pewter and measures 1" x 1-1/4" x 1-1/2".  She comes with an 8-32 x 1" machine screw for attaching to a cabinet door or drawer.  In spite of being and orphan with a Dickensian kittenhood, Sugar turned out to be a sweet  and well- balanced little cat.

name: Etta - Small Cat Knob
description: Etta is cast in non-leaded pewter and measures 1" x 1" x 1-1/4".  She comes with an 8-32 x 1" machine screw for mounting on a cabinet door or drawer.  Etta isn't the smartest cat around. but she hasn't a molecule of meaness in her small, silvery head.

name: Warren - Small Cat Head Knob
description: Warren appears angry, but he's not.  He just has that kind of face. He is cast in non-leaded pewter and measures 1" x 1-1/4" x 1-1/4".  He comes with an 8-32 x 1" machine screw for mounting him on a cabinet door or drawer.  If you put Warren in your house, you will find he will make you smile.

name: Felicia - Small Cat Head Knob
description: Felicia is cast in non-leaded pewter and measures 1-1/4" x 1-1/4" x 1-1/2".  An 8-32 x 1" machine screw is included for attaching her  to a cabinet door or drawer.  She has ulterior motives, but as yet, we don't know what they are.

name: Pie - Small Cat Head Knob
description: Pie is a sweet cat whose face is somewhat pie-shaped...hence the name.  He is cast in non-leaded pewter and comes with an 8-32 x 1" machine screw for fastening on to a cabinet door or drawer.  He'll make you smile and he's useful as well.

name: Moo-Shu - Small Cat Head Knob
description: Moo-Shu is a small cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter.  He comes with a 1" x 8-32 machine screw for fastening on to a cabinet door or drawer.  He's a bit of a gourmet and loves Beluga caviar, though any fish will do.

name: Marge Waterfowl Doorbell Cover
description:
Marge is a sweet bird who will pleasantly await visitors to your house.  Her eye is the doorbell button, which, when gently pressed, will make the doorbell ring.  Don't worry, she suffers from itchy eye syndrome, so she appreciates a touch to the eye now and then.

Marge measures 5" x 1-1/4" x 3/8" and is cast in bronze.  She comes with four brass screws for mounting and a 13/16" diameter gold rimmed doorbell push button.  For wired doorbells only.

name: Harvey Doorbell Cover
description: Harvey measures 3-1/2" x 2-1/2" x 1-1/8" and is cast in bronze.  When you press his nose, a doorbell rings.  His nose is attached to a rectangular doorbell button which his face fits over.  He comes with two brass screws for mounting to a door or wall.  Harvey is an inviting bloke and puts your visitors in a cheery mood, right away.  For wired doorbells only.

name: Percy Cat Doorbell Cover
description: This cat enjoys lying on his rug, getting some shut-eye.  He doesn't really care if someone comes and presses the doorbell.  He is content to stay put.  Percy is cast bronze and measures 2-1/8" x 2-1/2" x 5/8".  He comes with four brass screws for mounting on a door or wall.  A 13/16" diameter gold rimmed doorbell button is included.

name: Sparky Dog Doorbell Cover
description: Sparky lies comfortably on his dog bed waiting patiently for someone to come and ring his bell.  This cast bronze doorbell cover is 2-1/2" x 3" x 3/4"and comes with three brass screws for mounting to a door, molding or panel.  A 13/16" diameter gold rimmed doorbell push button is also included with Sparky.

name: Fiona Frog Doorbell Cover
description: Fiona is a cheerful bronze frog. She keeps a lighted, gold rimmed bell button in her mouth, but fear not, she is not dangerous...only delightful. She measures 2-5/8'' x 2'' x 1'' and comes with two brass screws for easy installation

name: Rupert Doorbell Cover
description: Rupert loves to sing! And so we made him a doorbell cover so he can sing out your visitor's arrival. He is cast in bronze and measures 2-1/4'' x 1-7/8'' x 3/4''.  Rupert comes with a gold-rimmed, lighted doorbell button and two brass screws for easy installation

name: Barbara Crow Doorbell Cover
description: Those brave enough to put their finger in Barbara's mouth and push the button will be rewarded with the chimes of a doorbell. Barbara is cast in bronze and comes with a lighted, gold rimmed doorbell button and two brass screws for easy installation.  She measures 3'' x 3'' x 2-3/4''.

name: Chaz Chameleon Doorbell Cover
description: Chaz is cast in bronze and comes with two brass screws for mounting on a wall. He can be secured in either a vertical or horizontal position.  Chaz measures 6-1/4'' x 2'' 3/8 '' .  His eye is a 13/16'' round, gold rimmed doorbell button which lights up. He may be a bit unexpected, but he's friendly and should put a smile on your visitor's face.

name: Garth Fish Doorbell Cover
description: Garth is cast in bronze and comes with two brass screws for mounting. His eye is a 13/16'' round, gold rimmed doorbell button that lights up.  He measures 5-1/2'' x 2'' x 3/8'' and can be attached to a wall vertically or horizontally.

name: Olga Octopus Hook
description: Olga Octopus has been cast in bronze and her eyes are two stainless steel screws which fasten her to a wall or door. Two of her legs create a versatile double hook. She measures 3-1/4'' x 4-1/4'' x 2-1/2''.  Olga is very sturdy and can be used in any setting, inside or outside.

name: Chaka Dog Hook
description: Chaka is cast in bronze and measures 2-3/8'' x 3-3/4'' x 2-1/2''.  Two brass screws are included for easy installation. She is an excellent hook for dog leashes as well as for more mundane things that need to be hung. Chaka can go inside or outside and adds pizazz to any surrounding.

name: Irv Hook
description: Irv has a big mustache that acts as a double hook. He measures 3" x 4" x 2" and is cast in bronze.  Two brass screws are included to attach him to a door or wall.  Irv is quite versatile (and friendly) and loves the indoors and outdoors, so put him in any setting and he'll be happy.

name: Dinah Elephant Hook
description: Dinah is a friendly and helpful elephant hook.  She measures 2'' x 1-3/4'' x 3'' and is cast in non-leaded pewter.  Two stainless steel wood screws are included for easy mounting to a wall or door..

name: Pablo Penguin Hook
description: Pablo found hs way from chilly environs to be of use in your warm home. He measures 2-1/2'' x 2-1/2'' x 2-1/4'' and is cast in non-leaded pewter.  Two stainless steel wood screws are included for easy installation.

name: Ike Moose Hook
description: Ike is cast in non-leaded pewter.  A threaded screw is cast within his stem for easy installation.  Ike measures 2-1/4" x 1-1/2" x 4".

name: Rabbit Hook - Mitzi
description: Kids actually like to hang up their clothes with Mitzi there to help. She is cast in non-leaded pewter and comes with two stainless wood screws for easy mounting. Mitzi measures 3" x 2" x 2".

name: Rabbit Hooks - Bernie
description: Kids actually like to hang up their clothes with Bernie there to help. He is cast in non-leaded pewter and  comes with two stainless wood screws for easy mounting.   He measures 2-1/4'' x 2-1/2'' x 2''.

name: Terrier - Sitting Dog Knob
description: Terrier is a cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter.  She measures 1-1/2" x 1-1/4" x 1-1/2" and comes with an 8-32 x 1" stainless steel machine screw for mounting on a door or drawer.

name: Lab - Sitting Dog Knog
description: Lab is a cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter.  She measures 1-3/4" x 1-1/2" x 1-1/4" and comes with an 8-32 x 1" stainless steel machine screw for mounting on a door or drawer.

name: Bulldog - Sitting Dog Knob
description: Bulldog is a cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter.  He measures 1-1/2" x 1" x 1-1/4" and comes with an 8-32 x 1" stainless steel machine screw for mounting on a door or drawer.

name: Shorthair - Sitting Dog Knob
description: Shorthair dog is a cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter.  He measures 2" x 1-1/4" x 1-1/2"and comes with an 8-32 x 1" stainless steel machine screw for mounting on a door or drawer.

name: Hopeful Mutt - Resting Dog Knob
description: Hopeful Mutt is a cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter.  He measures 1-1/4" x 1-3/4" x 1" and comes with an 8-32 x 1" stainless steel machine screw for mounting on a door or drawer.

name: Pensive Pup - Resting Dog Knob
description: Pensive Pup is a cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter.  He measures 3/4" x 1-3/4" x 1" and comes with an 8-32 x 1" stainless steel machine screw for mounting on a door or drawer.

name: Weiner Dog - Resting Dog Knob
description: Weiner Dog is a cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter.  He measures 1" x 2" x 1" and comes with an 8-32 x 1" stainless steel machine screw for mounting on a door or drawer.

name: Happy Lab - Resting Dog Knob
description: Happy Lab is a cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter. He measures 1" x 2" x 1-1/2". He comes with a 8-32 x 1" machine screw for fastening to a door or drawer.

name: Albert - small head knob
description: Albert is a small cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter. He measures 3/4" x 1" x 1-1/2". He comes with a 8-32 x 1" machine screw for fastening to a door or drawer.

name: Clara - Small Dog Head Knob
description: Clara is a small cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter. She measures 1" x 1" x 1-3/4". She comes with a 8-32 x 1" machine screw for fastening to a door or drawer.

name: Gordon - small head knob
description: Gordon is a small cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter. He measures 1-1/2" x 1-1/4" x 2". He comes with a 8-32 x 1" machine screw for fastening to a door or drawer.

name: Bob - small head knob
description: Bob is a small cabinet knob cast in non-leaded pewter.  He measures 1" x 1-1/4" x 1-1/2".  He comes with a 8-32 x 1" machine screw for fastening to a door or drawer.
